"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwangdoc=self.webpackChunkwangdoc||[]).push([[708],{95019:(n,e,a)=>{a.r(e),a.d(e,{data:()=>s});const s={key:"v-2338840c",path:"/git-tutorial/commands/git-log.html",title:"git log",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{summary:"git log git log命令按照提交时间从最晚到最早的顺序，列出所有 commit。 查看远程分支的变动情况。 查找log，即搜索commit信息。 上面代码中，-i参数表示搜索时忽略大小写。 查看某个范围内的commit 美化输出。 --graph commit之间将展示连线; --decorate 显示commit里面的分支; --pretty=o",head:[["meta",{property:"og:url",content:"https://yzqbooks.github.io/wangdoc/wangdoc/git-tutorial/commands/git-log.html"}],["meta",{property:"og:site_name",content:"wangdoc"}],["meta",{property:"og:title",content:"git log"}],["meta",{property:"og:type",content:"article"}],["meta",{property:"og:updated_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}],["meta",{property:"og:locale",content:"zh-CN"}],["meta",{property:"article:modified_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}]]},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"命令行参数",slug:"命令行参数",children:[{level:3,title:"--oneline",slug:"oneline",children:[]}]}],git:{createdTime:164923974e4,updatedTime:164923974e4,contributors:[{name:"yzqdev",email:"yzqdev@outlook.com",commits:1}]},readingTime:{minutes:.87,words:261},filePathRelative:"git-tutorial/commands/git-log.md"}},71422:(n,e,a)=>{a.r(e),a.d(e,{default:()=>o});const s=(0,a(66252).uE)('<h1 id="git-log" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#git-log" aria-hidden="true">#</a> git log</h1><p><code>git log</code>命令按照提交时间从最晚到最早的顺序，列出所有 commit。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 列出当前分支的版本历史</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> log\n\n<span class="token comment"># 列出某个文件的版本历史，包括文件改名</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> log --follow <span class="token punctuation">[</span>file<span class="token punctuation">]</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><p>查看远程分支的变动情况。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> log remote/branch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>查找log，即搜索commit信息。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> log --author<span class="token operator">=</span>Andy\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> log -i --grep<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">&quot;Something in the message&quot;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><p>上面代码中，<code>-i</code>参数表示搜索时忽略大小写。</p><p>查看某个范围内的commit</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> log origin/master<span class="token punctuation">..</span>new\n<span class="token comment"># [old]..[new] - everything you haven&#39;t pushed yet</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><p>美化输出。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">git</span> log --graph --decorate --pretty<span class="token operator">=</span>oneline --abbrev-commit\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><ul><li>--graph commit之间将展示连线</li><li>--decorate 显示commit里面的分支</li><li>--pretty=oneline 只显示commit信息的标题</li><li>--abbrev-commit 只显示commit SHA1的前7位</li></ul><h2 id="命令行参数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#命令行参数" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 命令行参数</h2><h3 id="oneline" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#oneline" aria-hidden="true">#</a> --oneline</h3><p><code>git log</code>默认输出每个 commit 的详细信息，为了节省空间，<code>--oneline</code>参数让输出时，每个 commit 只占用一行。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> log --oneline --decorate\nccc3333 <span class="token punctuation">(</span>HEAD, my-feature-branch<span class="token punctuation">)</span> A third commit\nbbb2222 A second commit\naaa1111 A first commit\n<span class="token number">9999999</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>master<span class="token punctuation">)</span> Old stuff on master\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div>',17),t={},o=(0,a(83744).Z)(t,[["render",function(n,e){return s}]])},83744:(n,e)=>{e.Z=(n,e)=>{const a=n.__vccOpts||n;for(const[n,s]of e)a[n]=s;return a}}}]);